        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "text": "5-2 ԓґٙ࿴ிၾ၇ᗳ"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "現代用途最廣的車床,不外是高速車床,如圖 5-2 示。"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "▲ ߧ 5-2 ȭネⳌⰇಉࡣ቏ᐉⳍ ( שʑᑨဏͧ ) 高速車床主要部位包括..主軸頭座 (Head-stock)、快速變換齒輪箱 (Quick-change gearbox)、 刀具溜座組 (Tool carriage assembly)、床台 (Bed) 及尾座 (Tail-stock) 等機構,分述如下。"
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "text": "ɓe˴ൿ᎘ࢭ"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "主軸頭座如圖 5-3 所示,包含空心主軸、主軸齒輪系及外掛齒輪系等三部分。"
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "text": "Ț ߧ 5-3 ȭʙⰧᆑಚ"
        }
      ],
      "page_image_url": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/thumb2086/AcademicTycoon_data/main/assets/content_pages/content_mech_basic_practice_ch05/p004.jpg"
    },
